<h1>CentOS - Available Repositories</h1>

<p>2011-11-25 00:00 星期五</p>

<p><a href="http://wiki.centos.org/AdditionalResources/Repositories" target="_blank">http://wiki.centos.org/AdditionalResources/Repositories</a></p>

<p>There are several repositories provided by CentOS and other 3rd party developers that offer software packages that are not included in the default base and updates repositories. While no list can be 100% complete, as anyone may announce an archive, it represents some major efforts and provides a summary of what each repository offers. These repositories have varying levels of stability, support and cooperation within the CentOS community.</p>

<p>CentOS 和其他提供软件开发包的第三方开发者们提供了一些库，但这些库不被包含在基础库和更新库中。没有一个100%的列表，因为任何人都可以宣布档案列表。这些库有不同程度的稳定性。</p>

<h2>3rd Party Repositories</h2>

<h3>RPMForge</h3>

<p>This repository is a collaboration of Dag (who also maintains an individual archive) and other packagers. The archive provides over 10,000 packages for CentOS, including mplayer, xmms-mp3 and other popular media tools. You can read the installation instructions at Installing RPMForge. This repository is considered by many in the community to be stable and safe.</p>

<p>This repository sometimes is referred to as DAG repository or similar.</p>

<p>这个库是 Dag 和其他包共同努力的结果。这个档案给 CentOS 提供了越过 10000 个包，包括 mplayer, xmms-mp3 和其它流行的媒体工具。你可以在安装 RPMForge 时阅读安装指令。这个库被社区的许多成员认为是稳定和安全的。</p>

<p>这个库有时也被认为是 DAG 库。</p>

<p>Mike strongly recommends using the supplied unversioned repos release rpm for auto-configuring this repository:</p>

<p>root@localhost:~# rpm -Uvh http://mhrepo.co.cc/pub/el/mhrepo-release.noarch.rpm</p>

<h3><strong>Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux (EPEL)</strong></h3>

<p><strong>2014-01-31 17:20 Friday</strong></p>

<p>This repository (See&nbsp;<a href="http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL">http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/EPEL</a>) provides rebuilds of Fedora packages for EL5 and EL6. Install the appropriate epel-release package for&nbsp;<a href="http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/5/i386/epel-release-5-4.noarch.rpm">EL5</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/i386/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm">EL6</a>&nbsp;to configure.&nbsp;This repo has made efforts not to replace system packages. In some cases it has endeavored to directly address CentOS compatibility but has expressly denied inter-repository compatibility as a goal. It may not mix well with other 3rd party repos. So, make SURE you are using the&nbsp;<a href="http://wiki.centos.org/PackageManagement/Yum/Priorities">Priorities</a>&nbsp;yum plugin if you are using EPEL ... especially if you mix its packages with those from other 3rd party repos. It should also be noted that, while EPEL may not overwrite distro packages, it may have conflicts with the CentOS extras repo which is enabled by default.</p>

<p>用浏览器打开此页 https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/x86_64/，即可看到所有可用软件包的列表，包括&nbsp;<a href="https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/x86_64/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm">epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm</a>。安装方法：</p>

<pre>
rpm -ivh&nbsp;http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/x86_64/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm</pre>

<p>可惜这里面仍然没有 php5.5</p>

<h3><strong>Les RPM de Remi repository</strong></h3>

<p><strong>2014-01-31 17:44 Friday</strong></p>

<p>(See&nbsp;<a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/">http://rpms.famillecollet.com/</a>) has been recommended on the mailing list and forum. Remi Collet maintains latest version of MySQL and PHP (backports of fedora RPM). Repo configs for&nbsp;<a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/enterprise/6/remi/i386/repoview/remi-release.html">EL6 i386</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/enterprise/6/remi/x86_64/repoview/remi-release.html">EL6 x86_64</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/enterprise/5/remi/i386/repoview/remi-release.html">EL5 i386</a>, and&nbsp;<a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/enterprise/5/remi/x86_64/repoview/remi-release.html">EL5 x86_64</a>&nbsp;as well as EL4 are available. Suggest caution if using this repo due to replacement of core packages.</p>

<p>Remi 维护着最新版本的 MySQL 和 PHP。</p>

<p><a href="http://rpms.famillecollet.com/enterprise/6/remi/x86_64/repoview/remi-release.html">EL6 x86_64</a>:</p>

